description:
Danny welcomes Emma and Julie from @CommentsbyCelebs! They break down everything that's going on in the world of celebrity and social media. They talk Shawn Mendes and Camila Cabello, Emmys, Britney, JLo's Versace dress, and SO much more in this special extra episode of Everything Iconic.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
